Quickly, the assassin leapt from where she was lying, dagger at the ready, only to be confronted with a woman. She was tall, taller than Kalasin 6”1’, which was saying a lot. The amazon frowned as she looked over her, wondering exactly where this woman had come from. However, it did not really matter. She quickly started to speak in Latin, which was to her at least, a universal language.<br>
<br>
“Who are you?”<br>
