 The panther, one Skada by name, walks over tot he two women, and noting the dagger in one's hand, she tosses a scroll she had in her mouth. It opens reveiling a message.<br>
       &quot;Yasoo Sisters,<br>
    Greetings, my name is Lalita Silver. The feline that has brought you this message is Skada. We send you this message as a greeting. I regret I am unable to meet you in person but I will be coming to the Crimson valley soon. Use whatever huts are still in good shape. <br>
  If there is any thing you need you have questions you would like answered, write them down and hand them to Skada, she will bring them to me.<br>
                Brightest Blessing on you,<br>
                       Lalita Silver                    &quot;<br>
<br>
The panther sits down and waits to see if they want anything answered. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=battlingangel>Battling Angel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 91<br> <font color=#993300>(6/1/03 2:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=44.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.speedis.org/images/188800.png WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Feline Welcome</span><hr size=1> Kalasin looked down at the feline briefly after her eyes flicked over the message. She was somewhat surprised, but managed to keep it well hidden. The assassin was not an animal lover. She looked back to the tall woman before her for a moment, and then back down at the creature and up again. <br>
<br>
&quot;Well, I don't have any questions aside from the identity of this one here&quot; The Shatomlic Amazon indicated the tall woman with her dagger.<br>
